Why choose ALI?

Why choose ALI?

   We are in Montreal!
     * Recognized as the educational capital of Canada
     * Montreal is ranked as one of the top 10 student city destination in
       2012
     * Has the second largest number of students (over 90,000) in North
       America, 21% of which are international students
     * The world’s most bilingual city in the world for English and French
     * Low cost of living

   Great location & Services!
     * ALI is in the heart of downtown, with modern and comfortable
       facilities.
     * Diversity of programs with dynamic and interactive classes and
       programs
     * Personalized attention; we take into account the needs of each
       student

   You will be studying with Canadians and practicing the language with
   people from all over the world.
     * Study English or French in Montreal, Canada
     * Study with Canadians
     * 25% of ALI students are Canadian and 75% are international students

   The ALI experience
