   Rudiger Bardges – Völklingen, Allemagne

   « ALI in Montreal is a really excellent language school for French and
   English. The teachers in charge are highly educated and passionately
   dedicated to teach foreign students in a manner that each student feels
   important and interested to give the best in class and outside class.
   The atmosphere is excellent and the attention extraordinary. I can only
   recommend ALI for students of all ages who are really interested in
   learning a new language. »
   Rudiger Bardges – Völklingen, Allemagne

